    "For our illustration, we consider the question of \"What does the well-being of a human depend on?",
    "\", as a well-known question on which there no general consensus on a particular answer but instead every culture generally provides an answer in more or less explicit terms.",
    "We consider situations in which an LLM generates as outputs a set of items out of some possiblylarger set of possibilities.",
    "For example, we might ask the LLM to (repeatedly) produce a list of 100 human languages, poets, animal species, or chemical compounds.",
    "The LLM generates this set based on a transformer, state-space model, etc."
  ],
